": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>确实是，路况不熟的人要左转的会提前好远变到左道</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "发糕爸爸", "author_id": "26cc34934a95627b0fea5cc0dd1de380", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "652488071", "reply_comment_id": "652347189", "reply_root_comment_id": "652347189", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "左道全线都是护栏啊，怎么转捏～", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}]}, {"url_token": "cctv27", "headline": "自由职业", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "671256581", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "671256581", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "昨天，邻道打右转想并过来，我稍微向前提了下车，他可能看出我原本不同意加塞，两车都怠速，那个车居然摇下车窗冲我笑着示意，看他那么有礼貌，果断让他并过来", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "知乎用户GD0aku", "author_id": "3390cf9a9feee46c05b8b59a0ebb78b4", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "671308178", "reply_comment_id": "671256581", "reply_root_comment_id": "671256581", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "互谅互让当然是最好的啦，有些人是非得强行别车加塞", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}]}, {"url_token": "hang-hang-90-48", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "642150185", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>这个防加塞的方法对于大多数情况还是很有用的，但有些不要脸的流氓仗着自己车破不怕怼，并且认定你会怂的，对这类流氓还是没有用，而且加塞的车足够流氓的话，会斜着用他的车头压住你的车头（因为你的车头相对于你排的队列是有点探出去的），这样你反而更加被动，防加塞最根本的办法还是尽量贴近前车，然后向相反的方向靠（左边有车会加塞进来，你的车就向右边靠），这样给加塞的车会留一点进来的空间，意思是告诉对方，你加别人的塞我不管，但你别想加我的塞，但前提是你跟前车跟的足够近，他是没法加塞到你前面的，可你后面的车就有极大可能就倒霉了，因为他达到了加塞的目的，不会死命来挤你的。最后说一句，希望大家开车都能贴紧前车，让加塞狗无路可走！</p>", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "夯夯", "author_id": "7439f6682a6cc5201cc860a69ba20d4b", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "lockdown-14", "headline": "但不要习惯了黑暗就为黑暗辩护，也不要为自己的苟且而得意。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "778268129", "reply_comment_id": "642150185", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "其实我也想说，放加塞是往来车反方向才对[握手]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Lockdown", "author_id": "c4feb045a5de534f5789810a8b7ba13d", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "shu-tian-chu", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "737276916", "reply_comment_id": "642150185", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对啊，这么搞你后面的就倒霉了。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "舒天楚", "author_id": "0bc8ad4d8d5e989a469a1739af34e44e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "bu-chi-xi-hong-shi-60", "headline": "不吃西红柿", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "691819791", "reply_comment_id": "642150185", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "精辟", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "不吃西红柿", "author_id": "ec7bbca8e999fddc6176b580fad12520", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "671309635", "reply_comment_id": "663593942", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "运钞车不是需要避让的特种车辆，而且我们这边的运钞车实线变道加塞，甚至堵住另外一条车道等着加塞，所以没必要让它", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "ren-zhi-jie-43", "headline": "牢骚太盛防肠断，风物长宜放眼量", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "663593942", "reply_comment_id": "642279997", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "运钞车你都不让，没下来拿枪突突你[飙泪笑]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "运输队长常凯申", "author_id": "404242b046760166a0e91dc34c764795", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "642279997", "reply_comment_id": "642150185", "reply_root_comment_id": "642150185", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "遇上不怕怼的车，怎么防它都有办法的。唯一能制住的就是硬怼。前段时间遇到过一辆运钞车实线插队，我抵死不让，有本事你就撞呗，后面运钞车服输了[调皮]", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}]}, {"url_token": "ye-kong-83-11", "headline": "Do Ur Wk", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "696200590", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "696200590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "不要歧视女司机，我岳父公司的一个女职工，车开的叫一个遛。倒车入库，侧旁停车从来不减速，一把成。只要比车身稍大的空都能整进去。有一次我去我岳父公司玩，我把车停货车位了，货车司机看是我的车没好意思说，就停我旁边卸货了。中午人家去吃饭的时候，我出来发现我车堵里了。还有点缝，我在那拧了半个小时没出来，没办法就去找这个姐姐，姐姐两下就给我开出来了。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "夜空", "author_id": "20c83f67dc8e25d2ed901516da06d912", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "696481376", "reply_comment_id": "696200590", "reply_root_comment_id": "696200590", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "我自己也是女司机，绝对木有歧视的意思。而且我自己开车开得不错，倒车从没出过问题。但从客观来说，确实有些女司机，但不是全部女司机哈，真的很奇怪。女人天生性格如此吧，比较胆小谨慎，开车有时候会受情绪影响。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}]}, {"url_token": "la-feng-ge-16-96", "headline": "物体表面硬度高分子保护", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "854378357", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "854378357", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "在重庆防加塞没用，你永远想不到开羚羊的司机是哪个车队退役的赛车手", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "拉风哥", "author_id": "0530cca9e681d7ca1a190dc36bb3d60d", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}]